Package: DiAna
Title: Advanced Disproportionality Analysis in the FAERS for Drug Safety
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michele", "Fusaroli", , "michele.fusaroli2@unibo.it", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0254-2212"))
Description: The `DiAna` (Disproportionality Analysis) package allows for
    downloading FAERS cleaned data, and import relational datasets.  It
    allows to identify cases and select controls to reduce confounding.
